cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CR, cs.AI 

This paper focuses on face anti-spoofing using a joint CNN-LSTM network to capture the temporal dynamics in videos. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses attention mechanism and eulerian motion magnification, which are related to machine learning and multimedia, respectively. Hence, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories. Additionally, since the paper deals with security and fraud detection, cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is another possible category.
